{"tid":1015710,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"跟「白人」交朋友慘遭霸凌：去死！　9歲黑人女童崩潰上吊自殺","createTime":"2019-02-10T08:53:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-10T09:22:01.000Z","uid":212399,"like":2,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"78197e71e88742303be46e81f86f75e8b32f3200","tid":1015710,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:53:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://pbs.twimg.com/media/DuL2kSCWkAAlBHF?format=jpg&amp;name=small\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpbs.twimg.com%2Fmedia%2FDuL2kSCWkAAlBHF%3Fformat%3Djpg%26name%3Dsmall&h=deb3842e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n國際中心／綜合報導<br />\n美國阿拉巴馬州一名9歲女孩妮可（McKenzie Nicole Adams）先前在學校，與一名白人男孩成為朋友，不過這段友情卻變成其他同學霸凌她的原因，她在2018年12月3月時終於忍受不了這種生活，選擇用自殺結束自己的生命，留下悲痛的家人。<br />\n根據外媒報導，這起悲劇發生在阿拉巴馬州的美國瓊斯小學（US Jones Elementary School），妮可先前就讀該間學校時，因為與一名白人男孩成為朋友，遭受其他同學異樣眼光的對待，這些人更對小小年紀的她說「你去自殺吧！跟白人男孩交朋友你就認為你是白人嗎？你這醜陋的黑人！去死一死吧！」<br />\n妮可在前一間學校曾經遭受過霸凌，後來轉學到現在的學校，沒想到與他人結交朋友，竟然會變成她被欺負的原因，成為壓倒她的最後一根稻草。2018年12月31日時，妮可選擇在家中房間裡上吊自殺，隨後被家人發現。<br />\n報導中指出，妮可的家人對於孩子的死非常傷心，她的阿姨哈里斯（Harris）表示，她要把侄女的死因公布出來，因為她想打擊校園霸凌，還有那麼多沒有發聲，但是卻在摩摩承受著這些痛苦的孩子。原本妮可一家人可以快快樂樂得過聖誕節，家人更連妮可的禮物都買好了，沒想到現在卻要面對著冷冰冰的遺體，悲傷地度過這個節日。<br />\n▼妮可（McKenzie Nicole Adams）。（圖／翻攝自gofundme）<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3805/3805362.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3805%2F3805362.jpg&h=2d48d237&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190210/1329555.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ettoday.net%2Fnews%2F20190210%2F1329555.htm&d=%2Fxbz1EbUF671EgN7am0E%2BJgFNMRZLCTiZeA0y1vO9n4%3D&h=21093b01\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.ettoday.net/news/20190210/1329555.htm</a>"},{"pid":"ba522ac42219cff4b10b1d6d7a58ec17c91c5972","tid":1015710,"uid":42188,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:55:08.000Z","msg":"nigga"},{"pid":"1bcf5892f4edd8875056f0f41fc4c99344d80354","tid":1015710,"uid":212399,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T08:55:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/pig2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e0c84a60557fe4b713f7c36e5c8caa9e779f9e0d","tid":1015710,"uid":165187,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:10:26.000Z","msg":"唔死都無用喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f409600e8b9afeb5abb7415b1804ede7ed18afe1","tid":1015710,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:16:31.000Z","msg":"抵死啦"},{"pid":"1792af91b7a3f6ba1acd1706957c34fc2c820233","tid":1015710,"uid":10240,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"力架真係麻煩<br />\n同蝗玻璃心仲差唔多"},{"pid":"77d8bb6cc3c854cc379d32e6f02e688e45a9ed9b","tid":1015710,"uid":43041,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1792af91b7a3f6ba1acd1706957c34fc2c820233","tid":1015710,"uid":10240,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:19:27.000Z","msg":"力架真係麻煩<br />\n同蝗玻璃心仲差唔多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:20:02.000Z","msg":"dna<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9970126b6eba34813e47f7ae95065e158b43b2f","tid":1015710,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-10T09:22:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://pic.cr173.com/up/2016-4/2016042510441996790.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpic.cr173.com%2Fup%2F2016-4%2F2016042510441996790.jpg&h=02f